===Pronunciation===
* {{fi-IPA|*}}
* {{rhymes|lang=fi|ɑnoɑ}}
* {{hyphenation|sa|no|a|lang=fi}}

===Verb===
{{fi-verb}}

# {{lb|fi|transitive|intransitive}} to [[say]], [[tell]] (''transitive'' → ''+ partitive or accusative'' "something", ''intransitive'' → ''+ elative'', "about something")
#: (''transitive usage'') '''''Sanoiko''' hän sen?''
#:: '''''Did''' she '''say''' it?''
#: (''intransitive usage'') '''''Sanoiko''' hän siitä mitään?''
#:: '''''Did''' she '''say''' anything about it?''

